flowchart TB
  S([Run bootstrap on new server]) --> ROOT{Root + safe target?}
  ROOT -->|no| FAIL([Abort - not a monitored VM])
  ROOT -->|yes| PR[Prompt: VM name, central IP,<br/>ES password masked]
  PR --> LOCK[Wait for apt locks]
  LOCK --> WAZ[Install + register Wazuh Agent 1514/1515]
  WAZ --> SUR[Install Suricata + EVE JSON]
  SUR --> FAL[Install Falco + Falcosidekick]
  FAL --> FB[Install Filebeat -> ES 9200 HTTPS]
  FB --> TG[Install Telegraf -> ES]
  TG --> CFG[Write host-identity forwarding config]
  CFG --> HEALTH{All services active?}
  HEALTH -->|no| RST[Restart + show status] --> HEALTH
  HEALTH -->|yes| PAY[Print ARIA asset payload<br/>source_config_json]
  PAY --> DONE([Ready to register in ARIA])
  classDef dec fill:#FEF3C7,stroke:#D97706,color:#0F172A;
  classDef act fill:#EFF6FF,stroke:#2563EB,color:#0F172A;
  class ROOT,HEALTH dec;
  class PR,LOCK,WAZ,SUR,FAL,FB,TG,CFG,PAY act;
